### ================== RUTAS SIN AUTENTICACIÓN (PUBLIC) ==================

### Obtener todas las reservas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/public

### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todas las reservas (protegido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear una nueva reserva (protegido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2024-10-20",
  "checkOutDate": "2024-10-25",
  "totalPrice": 1250000,
  "booking_status": "Confirmada",
  "guestId": 1,
  "roomId": 1
}

### Actualizar una reserva (protegido)
# Cambiar el estado de la reserva a 'Pagada'
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_status": "Pagada"
}

### Eliminar lógicamente una reserva (protegido)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}